PRay is a parallelized Raytracer that is supposed to run in a client-server mode via TCP sockets.

Camera control keys : (AZERTY keyboard)
 - mode : m
 - translations : q/d + s/z + f/r
 - rotations : a/e + arrow keys
 - print camera information : c

Dependences (to build and run on a GNU/Linux platform) :
 - CMake (2.6+)
 - make (or some CMake-supported IDE)
 - C++ compiler with C++11 & OpenMP support
 - pthread
 - SDL
 - tinyxml
